\c 28 Dhavhidhi anoraira Soromoni pamusoro petemberi 28Zvino Dhavhidhi akaunganidza paJerusaremu machinda ose aIsiâ€‘ raeri, machinda amarudzi, navakuru vamapoka aibatira mambo vachiita mapoka, navakuru vezviuru, navakuru vamazana, navatariri venhumbi dzose nepfuma yose yamambo navanakomana vake, pamwechete navaranda navane simba, varume vose voumhare. 2 Ipapo mambo Dhavhidhi akasimuka, akamira namakumbo ake, akati, "Chindinzwai hama dzangu, navanhu vangu! Kana ndirini, ndakanga ndichiti mumwoyo mangu ndichavakira areka yesungano yaJehovha nechitsiko chaMwari wedu imba yokuzorora; zvino ndakanga ndagadzira zvose zvokuvaka nazvo. 3 Asi Mwari akati kwandiri, `Iwe haufaniri kuvakira zita rangu imba, nokuti uri munhu wokurwa, wakateura ropa.' 4 Asi Jehovha, Mwari waIsiraeri, akanditsaura paimba yose yababa vangu kuti ndive mambo waIsiraeri nokusingaperi; nokuti akatsaura Judha kuti ave mutungamiriri; paimba yaJudha akatsaura imba yababa vangu akandifarira ini, akandiita mambo wavaIsiraeri vose. 5 Zvino pakati pavanakomana vangu vose (flokuti Jehovha akandipa vanakornana vazhinj i) akatsaura mwanakomana wangu Soromoni, kuti agare pachigaro choushe chaJehovha muna Isiraeri. 6 Akati kwandiri
